<HEADLINE> Jordan's Stock Market Closes 0.30 Point Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, December 6 (Xinhua) -- The price index on Jordan's
Amman Financial Market closed at 165.88 Sunday, 0.30 point
higher than Saturday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 1,018,366 Jordanian dinars (some 1,438,370
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of 629,003 shares changed hand. 
