<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 1500 GMT December 7 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PNOM PENH -- A group of Khmer Rouge commanders who surrendered
to the Royal Government of Cambodia last Friday arrived here
Monday from the Thai-Cambodia border at Preah Vihear and
Samlot. (Cambodia-Khmer Rouge)
</P>
