<TEXT>
<P>
Abu Dhabi, December 7 (Xinhua) -- Leaders of the member states
of the Gulf Cooperation Council (GCC) arrived here Monday for
their annual summit designed to boost regional cooperation in
various fields.
</P>
<P>
President of the United Arab Emirates (UAE) Sheikh Zayed
bin Sultan al-Nahyan greeted the leaders of the other five GCC
countries upon their arrival at the airport.
</P>
<P>
