Mian told Li that he has witnessed the great changes that have
taken place in China during his current visit. The people of
Pakistan take China's achievements as their own, he said.
</P>
<P>
Pakistan hopes to further its cooperation with China in the
judicial area, Mian noted.
</P>
<P>
Mian and his party arrived here today at the invitation of
SPC. 
