<HEADLINE> Flash: DPR Korea Win Men's Free Pistol Team Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, Decmeber 7 (Xinhua) -- The Democratic People's
Republic of Korea won the men's free pistol team event in a
total score of 1,680 points at the Asian Games here on Monday.
</P>
<P>
