<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, December 6 (Xinhua) -- Janne Ahonen of Finland edged
Olympic champion Kazuyoshi Funaki of Japan to win the champion in
the World Cup ski jumping in Chamonix, France on Sunday.
</P>
