<HEADLINE> Ito Confident to Beat Chinese Swimmers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, December 7 (Xinhua) -- Japanese national champion
Shunsuke Ito threw down the gauntlet on Monday when he said that
he is confident of beating his Chinese rivals in the men's
100-meter freestyle in the ongoing Asian Games.
</P>
<P>
"I'm confident to beat them in the men's 100m freestyle on
Wednesday," said Shunsuke through an interpretor, "I will give
them no chance."
</P>
