<HEADLINE> Bank of New Zealand Aims for Home Banking </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, December 7 (Xinhua) -- Bank of New Zealand (BNZ)
plans to
launch an Internet home banking service by the middle of next
year,
according to a Wellington-based newspaper.
</P>
<P>
