<HEADLINE> Chavez to Be Elected as New Venezuelan President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, December 6 (Xinhua) -- Hugo Chavez was elected Sunday
Venezuela's president for the next five years from 1999.
</P>
<P>
According to the first official bulletin released by the
National Electoral Council, Chavez won 64.86 percent of votes.
</P>
</TEXT>
